window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Bradley receives a second chance on a steampunk planet. </b></p> <p>The wondrous sights captivate, the gizmos fascinate, and it is all possible with steam. Attempting the wilds, Bradley experiences a dash of heart-pumping adventure that unlocks new opportunities and brings unwanted problems. With proper application, a bit of wit, and a dash of luck he might achieve greatness.&nbsp;</p> <p><b>Contains mature content. </b></p>"; 
